  "detailed_description": "It's Valentine's Day, and the flirtatious pink dolphin Inia is looking for a last-minute date. However, her best friend is tired of Inia settling for random strangers. She has to prove that they're a worthwhile candidate!<br><br><strong>Can you help Inia find a date that lives up to her friend's standards?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/f9ae9ef0a1264a6b99b357fa400656d9.poster.avif?t=1768038989\" width=520 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/f9ae9ef0a1264a6b99b357fa400656d9.webm?t=1768038989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/f9ae9ef0a1264a6b99b357fa400656d9.mp4?t=1768038989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>6 romanceable girls</strong><br>You're bound to find one, two, or maybe even six girls that are totally your type!<br></li><li><strong>Half visual novel, half RPG</strong><br>Unlike most dating sims, the route you get isn't determined by dialogue choices. What you do is actually more important than what you say.<br></li><li><strong>Vaporwave</strong><br>From the user interface to the soundtrack – everything got that <i>A E S T H E T I C</i>.<br></li><li><strong>Ocean Facts</strong><br>Unlock glossary entries containing real-world facts about the ocean as you play!<br></li><li><strong>Lesbian-Approved</strong><br>I made my lesbian friend play this and she thought it was good.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/6f49bacd574030a66fd8f5f155780e03.webp?t=1768038989\" width=315 height=60 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "It's Valentine's Day, and the flirtatious pink dolphin Inia is looking for a last-minute date. However, her best friend is tired of Inia settling for random strangers. She has to prove that they're a worthwhile candidate!<br><br><strong>Can you help Inia find a date that lives up to her friend's standards?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/f9ae9ef0a1264a6b99b357fa400656d9.poster.avif?t=1768038989\" width=520 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/f9ae9ef0a1264a6b99b357fa400656d9.webm?t=1768038989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/f9ae9ef0a1264a6b99b357fa400656d9.mp4?t=1768038989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>6 romanceable girls</strong><br>You're bound to find one, two, or maybe even six girls that are totally your type!<br></li><li><strong>Half visual novel, half RPG</strong><br>Unlike most dating sims, the route you get isn't determined by dialogue choices. What you do is actually more important than what you say.<br></li><li><strong>Vaporwave</strong><br>From the user interface to the soundtrack – everything got that <i>A E S T H E T I C</i>.<br></li><li><strong>Ocean Facts</strong><br>Unlock glossary entries containing real-world facts about the ocean as you play!<br></li><li><strong>Lesbian-Approved</strong><br>I made my lesbian friend play this and she thought it was good.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1536720/extras/6f49bacd574030a66fd8f5f155780e03.webp?t=1768038989\" width=315 height=60 /></span>",
